
o porting to Qt4 / KDE4
  - actions
  - toolbar
  - clipboard
  - drag & drop
  - porting of plugins
  - i18n
  - cmake targets
  - install targets and directories
  - mime types
  - support for 'visibility hidden'
  - online help
  - use svn graphics instead of pixmaps
  - namespace for mt/Thread -> Kwave::Thread
  - use QThread as base of mt/Thread, get rid of Asynchronous_Object.h
  - elimintate use of KDE3 compatibility layer
  - elimintate use of Qt3 compatibility layer

